sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/spa
    activate server
    server->>browser: HTML Document
    deactivate server    

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/main.css
    activate server
    server->>browser: CSS File
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/spa.js
    activate server
    server->>browser: JS File
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: Browser executes JS and fetches JSON from server

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server->>browser: JSON File
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: Browser executes callback and renders the data